data.description: Welcome Home! This property is perfect for entertaining. Upon entrance, the beautiful arched walls lead to a formal dining area which is also open to the living space and kitchen. It sits on a corner lot with a huge sunroom in the backyard that is wired for a TV & ceiling fans. The primary bedroom is massive with room for a sitting area. This home is located in the heart of Baytown, close to shopping, restaurants and the local hospital. The A/C unit was replaced last year and has new double panel storm windows throughout. Schedule your appointment for a showing and come see for yourself!
